oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pee Wee King and Redd Stewart: Smaller Image
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Collins Sisters; King, Pee Wee, 1914-2000; Leonard, Jack; Offset printing; Stewart, Redd;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising Pee Wee King and his band featuring Redd Stewart, Jack Leonard, the Collins Sisters, the New Golden West Cowboys, Jim Vest, Russ Caswell, and others. The negatives feature photographs of Pee Wee King, Redd Stewart, Jack Leonard, and the Collins Sisters and would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
